    <briefdescription>
<para>System that resets the hasUpdate flag on all ScoreObserverComponents. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Scheduled after the UI binding systems have consumed the update. This ensures that ScoreObserverComponent::hasUpdate() returns true for exactly one frame after a score change.</para>
